[SPEAKER_01] jednom francuskom pravicu

381
00:15:19,679 --> 00:15:20,799
[SPEAKER_01] ili poliliterature

382
00:15:20,799 --> 00:15:22,600
[SPEAKER_01] Raymond Kenoj, recimo,

383
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:23,320
[SPEAKER_01] stilske vježbe.

384
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:23,820
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

385
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:25,139
[SPEAKER_01] Imate još gomin od tih autora

386
00:15:25,139 --> 00:15:26,200
[SPEAKER_01] koji su shvatili upravo

387
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,399
[SPEAKER_01] da ograničenje je

388
00:15:27,399 --> 00:15:28,519
[SPEAKER_01] najveći izvor kreacije.

389
00:15:28,519 --> 00:15:28,639
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

390
00:15:28,639 --> 00:15:29,460
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno,

391
00:15:29,460 --> 00:15:31,820
[SPEAKER_01] arbitrarno

392
00:15:31,820 --> 00:15:32,639
[SPEAKER_01] izabrati nekako

393
00:15:32,639 --> 00:15:33,659
[SPEAKER_01] ograničenje nekog dijela

394
00:15:33,659 --> 00:15:34,799
[SPEAKER_01] i onda unutar tog okvira,

395
00:15:34,799 --> 00:15:35,580
[SPEAKER_01] formalnog okvira,

396
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:36,940
[SPEAKER_01] biti što je moguće kreativno.

397
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

398
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,259
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne ide se za onim,

399
00:15:38,259 --> 00:15:38,899
[SPEAKER_01] kako se kaže,

400
00:15:38,899 --> 00:15:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] anything else postmoderno,

401
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,759
[SPEAKER_01] da se može poigrava

402
00:15:41,759 --> 00:15:42,460
[SPEAKER_01] svin i svačin,

403
00:15:42,460 --> 00:15:43,840
[SPEAKER_01] nego baš zadana forma

404
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] daje najizvrsniji,

405
00:15:44,820 --> 00:15:45,580
[SPEAKER_01] najbolji sadršaj.

406
00:15:45,580 --> 00:15:47,580
[SPEAKER_01] Vratimo se trenutak

407
00:15:47,580 --> 00:15:48,720
[SPEAKER_01] na jednu knjigu

408
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:50,139
[SPEAKER_01] koja je okosnica,

409
00:15:50,139 --> 00:15:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] koja je, možemo tako reći,

410
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] metatekst.

411
00:15:52,139 --> 00:15:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo se izraziti

412
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:55,179
[SPEAKER_01] teoretski.

413
00:15:55,179 --> 00:15:56,639
[SPEAKER_01] Svih Marulićeg dijela,

414
00:15:56,639 --> 00:15:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] gotovo svih Marulićeg dijela,

415
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:58,580
[SPEAKER_01] to je Biblija.

416
00:15:58,580 --> 00:16:01,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pitanje,

417
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] ako ga dobro razumijem,

418
00:16:04,179 --> 00:16:04,639
[SPEAKER_00] glasi,

419
00:16:04,639 --> 00:16:07,080
[SPEAKER_00] zašto Marulić

420
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] toliko citira Bibliju

421
00:16:08,980 --> 00:16:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] i samo Bibliju.

422
00:16:09,980 --> 00:16:11,360
[SPEAKER_01] Nadahnut,

423
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] nadahnutom Božem riječi.

424
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je pitanje

425
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] na koje nije lako odgovoriti,

426
00:16:18,139 --> 00:16:18,860
[SPEAKER_00] ali,

427
00:16:18,860 --> 00:16:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] ili koje bolje rečeno,

428
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:21,120
[SPEAKER_00] ima nekoliko odgovora.

429
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ćete naći

430
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:23,740
[SPEAKER_00] kod njegovih suvremenika,

431
00:16:23,740 --> 00:16:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] takozvanih kršanskih humanista,

432
00:16:26,039 --> 00:16:27,120
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

433
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,879
[SPEAKER_00] uvodima jedan pojam

434
00:16:28,879 --> 00:16:30,259
[SPEAKER_00] koji možda nije svakom poznat,

435
00:16:30,259 --> 00:16:32,279
[SPEAKER_00] nisu ovi drugi humaništi

436
00:16:32,279 --> 00:16:33,200
[SPEAKER_00] ne kršanski.

437
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:33,620
[SPEAKER_00] Znate,

438
00:16:33,620 --> 00:16:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] renesansa nije,

439
00:16:34,519 --> 00:16:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je rekao

440
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:36,600
[SPEAKER_00] jedan francoski filozof,

441
00:16:36,879 --> 00:16:38,740
[SPEAKER_00] srednji vijek bez Boga.

442
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] To je gruba simplifikacija.

443
00:16:41,019 --> 00:16:41,279
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

444
00:16:41,279 --> 00:16:42,700
[SPEAKER_00] i drugi humanisti su vjernici

445
00:16:42,700 --> 00:16:44,720
[SPEAKER_00] i samo što u njihovim dijelima

446
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] je svjetovni aspekt

447
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,220
[SPEAKER_00] i svjetovne teme

448
00:16:47,220 --> 00:16:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] su zastupljenije

449
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] nego kod nekih drugih.

450
00:16:49,519 --> 00:16:51,620
[SPEAKER_00] Među kršanske humaniste

451
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:52,700
[SPEAKER_00] se ubraja Petrarka,

452
00:16:52,700 --> 00:16:54,340
[SPEAKER_00] to možda ne biste očekivali

453
00:16:54,340 --> 00:16:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] kad mislite samo na kanconjera,

454
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,580
[SPEAKER_00] ali treba misliti na cijelog Petrarka.

455
00:16:57,580 --> 00:16:59,080
[SPEAKER_00] Ubraja se Lorenzo Vala,

456
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:00,600
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bio filolog i izvrstan,

457
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:02,139
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg je Marulić čitao,

458
00:17:02,139 --> 00:17:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] naravno i Petrarko je čitao

459
00:17:03,559 --> 00:17:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] i prevodio.

460
00:17:04,539 --> 00:17:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ubraja se prvak svih humanista

461
00:17:06,420 --> 00:17:07,640
[SPEAKER_00] Erasmur Otardapski.

462
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:11,359
[SPEAKER_00] Oni citiraju Bibliju,

463
00:17:11,359 --> 00:17:14,740
[SPEAKER_00] citiraju crkvene oce

464
00:17:14,740 --> 00:17:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] i citiraju poganske autore.

465
00:17:16,819 --> 00:17:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] Marulić kad citira,

466
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:20,240
[SPEAKER_00] onda citira samo Bibliju.

467
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] On se poziva na crkvene oce,

468
00:17:22,579 --> 00:17:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] narošta na Jeronima,

469
00:17:23,619 --> 00:17:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] često kaže,

470
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:25,740
[SPEAKER_00] kao što kaže naš Jeronim,

471
00:17:25,740 --> 00:17:27,599
[SPEAKER_00] tako imate na jednom lijepom mjestu.

472
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:28,440
[SPEAKER_00] U četku institucije.

473
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da, i u dehumilitate,

474
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] isto poniznosti Slavik Hristovoj.

475
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:34,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako treba citirati,

476
00:17:34,119 --> 00:17:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] izravno citira Bibliju.

477
00:17:35,420 --> 00:17:35,839
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

478
00:17:35,839 --> 00:17:37,220
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što je Biblija

479
00:17:37,220 --> 00:17:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] vrhunski autoritet

480
00:17:38,420 --> 00:17:40,200
[SPEAKER_00] i zato što je on,

481
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:40,819
[SPEAKER_00] naravno,

482
00:17:40,819 --> 00:17:43,140
[SPEAKER_00] nevjerojatno dobar poznavalost Biblije.

483
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, u ono vrijeme su se citati često

484
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:49,839
[SPEAKER_00] ili gotovo redovito izvodili iz sjećanja.

485
00:17:49,839 --> 00:17:53,339
[SPEAKER_00] Nije kao danas da ste vi išli provjerati točan citat,

486
00:17:53,339 --> 00:17:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] nego memoriralo se.

487
00:17:54,940 --> 00:17:56,779
[SPEAKER_00] Drugačiji je bio pristup u učenju

488
00:17:56,779 --> 00:17:59,059
[SPEAKER_00] i memoriranju.

489
00:17:59,059 --> 00:18:00,799
[SPEAKER_00] Strašno puno se toga znalo napaviti.

490
00:18:00,799 --> 00:18:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, šite nekada ti njegovi citati

491
00:18:02,559 --> 00:18:03,819
[SPEAKER_00] ni prema vulgati,

492
00:18:03,819 --> 00:18:04,859
[SPEAKER_00] ni su baš sasvim točni.

493
00:18:04,859 --> 00:18:06,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on je to imao

494
00:18:06,779 --> 00:18:10,440
[SPEAKER_00] i gradio je tu svoju argumentacijsku mrežu,

495
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,180
[SPEAKER_00] da tako kažemo,

496
00:18:11,180 --> 00:18:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] o pomoću Biblije.

497
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:15,240
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan moj kolega je to zgodno usporedio,

498
00:18:15,240 --> 00:18:16,799
[SPEAKER_00] malo neobično,

499
00:18:16,799 --> 00:18:18,259
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne sasvim pogrešno,

500
00:18:18,259 --> 00:18:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] s onim što se danas u popularnoj glazbi zove sem planje.

501
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:26,200
[SPEAKER_00] Da u svoju kompoziciju ubacujete niz kratkih citata

502
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,799
[SPEAKER_00] iz tuđih kompozicija.

503
00:18:27,799 --> 00:18:29,740
[SPEAKER_00] I to nikome ne smeta.

504
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:32,200
[SPEAKER_00] Njegovoj, Marulićovoj citateljskoj publici,

505
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] nije nimalo smetalo da on tako radi argumentaciju.

506
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sama institucija je protkana svim tim kompilacijama,

507
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:39,740
[SPEAKER_01] preuzimanjima,

508
00:18:39,740 --> 00:18:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] koje iz današnje perspektive možda djeluju pod navodnicima

509
00:18:41,940 --> 00:18:44,359
[SPEAKER_01] nečasno, ne navode se autori.

510
00:18:44,359 --> 00:18:45,759
[SPEAKER_01] To je, da, to je.

511
00:18:45,759 --> 00:18:49,420
[SPEAKER_01] Fraziraju se, ali suditi pod našim standardnima,

512
00:18:49,420 --> 00:18:53,980
[SPEAKER_01] našim tehničkim mjerilima i načinima pisanja,

513
00:18:53,980 --> 00:18:56,759
[SPEAKER_01] bilo književno, bilo znanstvenog dijela je sasvim, sasvim deplasirano.

514
00:18:56,759 --> 00:18:59,220
[SPEAKER_00] Dotaknuli ste, silno opristite što prekidam.

515
00:18:59,220 --> 00:19:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] Silno važno pitanje, a to je potrebu da se osvijesti jedna bitna stvar.

516
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:09,779
[SPEAKER_00] Pojmovi književnosti danas i u Marulićovo vrijeme su potpuno drugačiji.

517
00:19:09,779 --> 00:19:11,700
[SPEAKER_00] Opsek toga što je književnost.

518
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:16,799
[SPEAKER_00] Naš pojam književnosti je negdje od romantizma na ovamo definiran.

519
00:19:16,799 --> 00:19:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] Prije toga književnost je bila naravno ono što je pisano u stihu,

520
00:19:20,980 --> 00:19:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] to znači poezija i drama koja se pisala u stihu,

521
00:19:23,319 --> 00:19:27,160
[SPEAKER_00] a u prozi zapravo sve što je pisano dotjeranim stilom.

522
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:30,259
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u to ulazi i povijest, u to ulazi i teologija,

523
00:19:30,259 --> 00:19:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] u to ulazi čak i neke rasprave o, recimo, o graditeljstvu.

524
00:19:34,559 --> 00:19:37,700
[SPEAKER_00] Vitruvije u rimskoj književnosti spada u književnost,

525
00:19:37,700 --> 00:19:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] iako piše rasprav arhitekturi.

526
00:19:39,460 --> 00:19:44,259
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i prirodoznanstveni spisi se mogu ubrojiti u literaturu.

527
00:19:44,259 --> 00:19:46,299
[SPEAKER_00] To treba imati na pameti.

528
00:19:46,299 --> 00:19:47,619
[SPEAKER_01] Na stilskoj razini.

529
00:19:47,619 --> 00:19:51,160
[SPEAKER_00] I na stilskoj razini i na tome kako se to čita,

530
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] kako percipira čitalaca.

531
00:19:52,940 --> 00:19:57,160
[SPEAKER_01] Obzirom da naš razgovor o Maruliću je upućen prije svega

532
00:19:57,160 --> 00:20:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] vjeru učiteljima, ali i profesorima hrvatskog jezika

533
00:20:00,019 --> 00:20:02,900
[SPEAKER_01] i književnosti, općenito profesorima strednjoškolskima,

534
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:07,839
[SPEAKER_01] možemo se ukratko svrnuti na njegova dva središnja dijela,

535
00:20:07,839 --> 00:20:09,579
[SPEAKER_01] gotovo onaj poznatije uspješnice,

536
00:20:09,579 --> 00:20:11,839
[SPEAKER_01] to su institucija evanđelista.

537
00:20:11,839 --> 00:20:15,099
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu li ta dva dijela braća blizanci?

538
00:20:15,099 --> 00:20:18,119
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno, ne pretpostavljali jedan drugo?

539
00:20:18,119 --> 00:20:21,579
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo li kazati da je Marulić ono što je u jednoj formi,

540
00:20:21,579 --> 00:20:23,839
[SPEAKER_01] na jedan način ponudio evanđelistaru,

541
00:20:23,839 --> 00:20:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] na neki drugi način plasirao u obličju i ponudio instituciju?

542
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:31,720
[SPEAKER_00] Sinoptički.

543
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:34,319
[SPEAKER_00] Braća jesu, ali blizanci baš i ne.

544
00:20:34,319 --> 00:20:38,700
[SPEAKER_00] To je točno što vi kažete da je ono što je, dakle,

545
00:20:38,700 --> 00:20:42,180
[SPEAKER_00] u instituciji ponuđeno u obliku nizanja primjera,

546
00:20:42,180 --> 00:20:44,339
[SPEAKER_00] egzemplarnih priča.

547
00:20:47,059 --> 00:20:55,759
[SPEAKER_00] ista građa, isti mislani sklop, ista intencija moralno-etička živi u evanđelistaru,

548
00:20:55,759 --> 00:21:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali u evanđelistaru u obliku malih kratkih rasprava,

549
00:21:01,039 --> 00:21:07,299
[SPEAKER_00] argumentacijskih tema, u kojima se, dakle, ne iznose uzorni primjeri,

550
00:21:07,380 --> 00:21:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] nego se o jednoj temi raspravlja, donose se dokazi iz Biblije u prvom redu

551
00:21:13,539 --> 00:21:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] i na neki način diskurzivno se govori o tome što treba, što ne treba raditi.

552
00:21:20,380 --> 00:21:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli Marulić je zasnovan na tome da se slijede vrline,

553
00:21:24,779 --> 00:21:26,660
[SPEAKER_00] a izbjegavaju poroci.

554
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] Na to se može svesti 90 i više posto njegovog opusa.

555
00:21:32,940 --> 00:21:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, institucija i evanđelistari jesu na taj način slični,

556
00:21:37,099 --> 00:21:42,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali donekto su različiti po ciljanoj publici.

557
00:21:42,099 --> 00:21:47,779
[SPEAKER_00] Evanđelistari je pisan, dano gdje smo rekli, malo stručnije i malo zahtjevnije.

558
00:21:47,779 --> 00:21:48,660
[SPEAKER_00] Uđbenički.

559
00:21:48,819 --> 00:21:54,799
[SPEAKER_00] Uđbenički namijen je, to vidite iz teksta, jer se to pojavljene na više mjesta,

560
00:21:54,799 --> 00:21:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] namijen je u prvom redu crkvenim ljudima, dakle svećenicima,

561
00:21:58,539 --> 00:21:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] biskupima, redovnicima.

562
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo njima, nego i obrazovanim lajcima, jer ima poglavlja nama vrlo zanimljivih

563
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] o odgoju djece, o braku, o izboru žene.

564
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:10,779
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, očito za lajičku publiku.

565
00:22:10,779 --> 00:22:13,259
[SPEAKER_00] To je samo nekoliko poglavlja, ali ipak pokazuje.

566
00:22:13,259 --> 00:22:18,259
[SPEAKER_00] A institucija je jednostavnije pisana za širu publiku,

567
00:22:18,259 --> 00:22:23,839
[SPEAKER_00] i jako je praktična, recimo, propovjednicima, jer u njoj mogu naći građu,

568
00:22:23,839 --> 00:22:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] i to se pokazalo u povijesti, da su to i radili, građu za propovjedi.

569
00:22:27,420 --> 00:22:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je tolika količna, više od tisuću tih primjernih priča,

570
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, na taj način može pragmatično poslužiti.

571
00:22:34,420 --> 00:22:37,700
[SPEAKER_01] Da, kao neki homiletski priručnik.

572
00:22:37,700 --> 00:22:43,259
[SPEAKER_00] Da, kao neki izvor za, ako nemate ideje o čemu ćete propovjedati.

573
00:22:43,420 --> 00:22:46,819
[SPEAKER_01] Pedagogi se govori o afirmativnom govoru prema učenicima,

574
00:22:46,819 --> 00:22:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] prema bilo kome koje je objekt, grubo reći,

575
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] objekt nekakog odgoje obrazovanja.

576
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:55,200
[SPEAKER_01] U smislu da se uvijek ide za tim, da se i nečije mane pokažu svjetlu vrline,

577
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:57,680
[SPEAKER_01] koju on može dobiti ili je posjedio u jedan drugčiji način.

578
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] Naradili Marulić upravo to,

579
00:22:59,380 --> 00:23:02,160
[SPEAKER_01] iako nađećemo i kod njega upozoravanja na poroke,

580
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] nekakav kritički govor,

581
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:07,059
[SPEAKER_01] a nije li to svjetlo koje on baca na pozitivne strane,

582
00:23:07,059 --> 00:23:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] na vrline koje čovjek treba imati i posjedovati u skladu s tim?

583
00:23:10,579 --> 00:23:15,319
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da on pedagoški optimist, da, da se može...

584
00:23:15,319 --> 00:23:15,740
[SPEAKER_00] Humanist?

585
00:23:15,740 --> 00:23:20,839
[SPEAKER_00] Da, humanist, apsolutno, čujte, to je, dakle, vjera u čovjeka.

586
00:23:20,839 --> 00:23:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ste možda onaj humanist više svjetovnog tipa,

587
00:23:25,079 --> 00:23:29,640
[SPEAKER_00] onda će vaše usmjeravanje, argumentacija možda biti više uprevena

588
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:31,759
[SPEAKER_00] prema građanskom životu,

589
00:23:31,759 --> 00:23:36,700
[SPEAKER_00] a primjeri koje ćete pokazati su možda primjeri starih Grka i Rimljana,

590
00:23:36,700 --> 00:23:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] prema Plutarhu i prema Liviju, recimo.

591
00:23:39,500 --> 00:23:42,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ste kršanski humanist, onda ćete više usmjeriti

592
00:23:42,259 --> 00:23:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] prema kršanskom životu u ideal,

593
00:23:44,559 --> 00:23:48,240
[SPEAKER_00] a primjera će vam kao kod Marulića više biti

594
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:51,140
[SPEAKER_00] od svetačkih junaka, a ne od onih antičkih.

595
00:23:51,140 --> 00:23:54,880
[SPEAKER_01] Peter Zloderdajk, njemački filozof, govori da je

596
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:57,880
[SPEAKER_01] humanizam razdoblje odgoja pismom,

597
00:23:57,880 --> 00:24:00,160
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno prijateljevanja pismom.

598
00:24:00,700 --> 00:24:02,700
[SPEAKER_01] drugim riječima i Marulić je takav i on je svojim

599
00:24:02,700 --> 00:24:05,640
[SPEAKER_01] prijateljima iz humanističkog kruga upočivao pisma,

600
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,660
[SPEAKER_01] dopisivao se s njima.

601
00:24:06,660 --> 00:24:09,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad kažemo prijateljevanje pismom,

602
00:24:09,680 --> 00:24:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] biti humanizma je uvjerenje da se čovjeka može

603
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:14,400
[SPEAKER_01] oboljšati, odgojiti,

604
00:24:14,400 --> 00:24:15,680
[SPEAKER_01] popraviti kako god,

605
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:16,859
[SPEAKER_01] pisanom riječju.

606
00:24:16,859 --> 00:24:18,640
[SPEAKER_01] Marulić to nadograđuje Biblijom,

607
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:21,079
[SPEAKER_01] na kojoj smo se malo preosvrnili,

608
00:24:21,079 --> 00:24:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] govoreći da se čovjeka može

609
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:24,940
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo nadograditi odgojno obrazovno,

610
00:24:24,940 --> 00:24:26,900
[SPEAKER_01] već spasiti, dovesti do blaženstva.

611
00:24:26,900 --> 00:24:29,259
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, u religijalim smislu Božjem riječu.

612
00:24:29,259 --> 00:24:31,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to je onaj njegov aspekt

613
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji je najvidljiviji.

614
00:24:33,619 --> 00:24:35,779
[SPEAKER_00] Moram reći da postoji drugi aspekt,

615
00:24:35,779 --> 00:24:37,940
[SPEAKER_00] to je onaj Marulić iz latinskih epigrama.

616
00:24:37,940 --> 00:24:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] Glazgovskih.

617
00:24:38,940 --> 00:24:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] Glazgovskih.

618
00:24:39,940 --> 00:24:43,140
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su otvorili u velikoj mjeri,

619
00:24:43,140 --> 00:24:44,180
[SPEAKER_00] naravno, tog, recimo,

620
00:24:44,180 --> 00:24:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] ujetno drugog Marulića.

621
00:24:46,619 --> 00:24:48,200
[SPEAKER_00] Taj Marulić je, znate,

622
00:24:48,200 --> 00:24:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] nekad mediteranski zločest jednostavno

623
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] i svojim sugrađanima,

624
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:54,299
[SPEAKER_00] a i nekima udaljenijima,

625
00:24:54,299 --> 00:24:56,200
[SPEAKER_00] pa i nekim uglednicima,

626
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo oštrim jezikom privovara mane

627
00:24:59,119 --> 00:25:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] i uopće ne razmišlja o njihovom spasenju,

628
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] nego samo gleda kako da ih što zločestije

629
00:25:05,099 --> 00:25:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] i što elegantnije u izrazu ošine svojom kritikom.

630
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,579
[SPEAKER_01] Što nam to govori?

631
00:25:09,579 --> 00:25:10,480
[SPEAKER_01] O majstoru žandra,

632
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:13,500
[SPEAKER_01] koji je služeći sa razdoraznim pradošcima,

633
00:25:13,619 --> 00:25:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] žanrovskim, genealožički govoreći o kategorijama,

634
00:25:18,079 --> 00:25:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] znao nekad mijenjati stavu?

635
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znao je mijenjati pristup...

636
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:23,660
[SPEAKER_00] Neko će mu to uzeti za zlo,

637
00:25:23,660 --> 00:25:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] da nas šalim se, šalit se.

638
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] Da, znao je mijenjati pristup

639
00:25:26,859 --> 00:25:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] ovisno o tome u kojem žanru piše,

640
00:25:29,440 --> 00:25:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] kao što si rekli,

641
00:25:30,220 --> 00:25:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] i za koju publiku je to što piše namijenjeno.

642
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ako piše latinski epigram,

643
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] onda neizbježno mora nasljedovati

644
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] majstora, uzornog autora epigrama,

645
00:25:40,460 --> 00:25:42,200
[SPEAKER_00] to je rimski pjesnik Marcian,

646
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg on izvrsno poznaje,

647
00:25:43,880 --> 00:25:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] tako što poznaje i Ovidija,

648
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] ne biste rekli,

649
00:25:47,079 --> 00:25:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] on ljubavno umijeće,

650
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] tako reći,

651
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] napam,

652
00:25:49,900 --> 00:25:51,319
[SPEAKER_00] da znaju u zrelim godinama.

653
00:25:51,319 --> 00:25:52,140
[SPEAKER_00] To se vidi,

654
00:25:52,140 --> 00:25:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer pjesnici u ono vrijeme

655
00:25:54,380 --> 00:25:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] se bez ikakvog zazora

656
00:25:56,980 --> 00:25:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] služe

657
00:25:57,579 --> 00:25:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] svom memorijom,

658
00:25:59,619 --> 00:26:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] da pače to se smatra i pohvalnim,

659
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:03,220
[SPEAKER_00] da vi na taj način pokažete

660
00:26:03,220 --> 00:26:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] svoju učenost,

661
00:26:04,099 --> 00:26:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] otvorite jednu igru čitalca i autora,

662
00:26:07,099 --> 00:26:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je igra prepoznavanja,

663
00:26:09,079 --> 00:26:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] aha,

664
00:26:09,500 --> 00:26:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] vidiš,

665
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:11,240
[SPEAKER_00] u ovome podsjećena Ovidija,

666
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] on je dakle isto to čitao,

667
00:26:13,059 --> 00:26:14,819
[SPEAKER_00] igramo se te igre prepoznavanja.

668
00:26:14,819 --> 00:26:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

669
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] u tome je Marulić majstor

670
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:19,200
[SPEAKER_00] i u tome ne treba vidjeti ništa loše,

671
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] prilagođavanje publici

672
00:26:21,880 --> 00:26:25,559
[SPEAKER_00] je još u propovjedanju

673
00:26:25,559 --> 00:26:26,839
[SPEAKER_00] u starokršćanskoj

674
00:26:26,839 --> 00:26:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] bilo na čelo

675
00:26:28,119 --> 00:26:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] sermo coaptandus

676
00:26:29,559 --> 00:26:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] kvalitati auditorom.

677
00:26:31,099 --> 00:26:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

678
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:33,160
[SPEAKER_00] propovjed treba

679
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] prilagoditi

680
00:26:34,420 --> 00:26:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] kako oči slušatelja.

681
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:37,160
[SPEAKER_00] To možete primijeniti

682
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo na propovjed,

683
00:26:38,420 --> 00:26:39,339
[SPEAKER_00] nego na svaku drugu

684
00:26:39,339 --> 00:26:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] kljiževnu vrstu.

685
00:26:40,119 --> 00:26:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

686
00:26:41,619 --> 00:26:43,799
[SPEAKER_01] Vratimo se na kratko

687
00:26:43,799 --> 00:26:44,839
[SPEAKER_01] o nepoznatom Maruliću.

688
00:26:44,839 --> 00:26:45,759
[SPEAKER_01] Donadano smo imali,

689
00:26:45,759 --> 00:26:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] ako se ne varam,

690
00:26:46,579 --> 00:26:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] prije 5-6 godina,

691
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] možda čak i nešto više,

692
00:26:49,079 --> 00:26:50,259
[SPEAKER_01] sveća da me baš dobro ne služi.

693
00:26:50,259 --> 00:26:51,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nekakav javni prijepor

694
00:26:51,460 --> 00:26:52,299
[SPEAKER_01] koji se je rodio

695
00:26:52,299 --> 00:26:53,640
[SPEAKER_01] iz prijedloga

696
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,200
[SPEAKER_01] koji je došao

697
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:55,480
[SPEAKER_01] iz Ministarstva obrazovanja

698
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:56,640
[SPEAKER_01] o tome da se revidira

699
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,640
[SPEAKER_01] literatura

700
00:26:57,640 --> 00:26:58,880
[SPEAKER_01] koja će se dao djeci

701
00:26:58,880 --> 00:27:00,099
[SPEAKER_01] za lektiru

702
00:27:00,099 --> 00:27:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] u srednjim i osnovnim školama

703
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] i došlo se do

704
00:27:02,579 --> 00:27:04,279
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno jednog prijedloga

705
00:27:04,279 --> 00:27:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] imali Maruliću mjesta

706
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:06,200
[SPEAKER_01] u tomu svemu.

707
00:27:06,200 --> 00:27:07,519
[SPEAKER_01] Razlozi,

708
00:27:07,519 --> 00:27:09,240
[SPEAKER_01] razlozi za takvo propitivanje

709
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:09,940
[SPEAKER_01] koje po meni

710
00:27:09,940 --> 00:27:11,480
[SPEAKER_01] možemo se nakratko

711
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:12,259
[SPEAKER_01] kasnije usvrljiti

712
00:27:12,259 --> 00:27:13,240
[SPEAKER_01] zašto je

713
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:14,759
[SPEAKER_01] sasvim, sasvim neutemeljeno

714
00:27:14,759 --> 00:27:16,500
[SPEAKER_01] jes njegova nepripstupačnost,

715
00:27:16,500 --> 00:27:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] stari jezik,

716
00:27:17,539 --> 00:27:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] nerazumljivosti djeci,

717
00:27:20,079 --> 00:27:22,319
[SPEAKER_01] obojenost religijskog diskursa,

718
00:27:22,319 --> 00:27:23,200
[SPEAKER_01] svjetonazorska,

719
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:24,259
[SPEAKER_01] pristranost njegova

720
00:27:24,259 --> 00:27:24,779
[SPEAKER_01] i tako da.

721
00:27:24,779 --> 00:27:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] Što mislite to?

722
00:27:26,559 --> 00:27:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da inače

723
00:27:28,079 --> 00:27:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] ima puno nevolja

724
00:27:29,380 --> 00:27:30,700
[SPEAKER_00] sa našim kurikulom

725
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] i sa našom lektirom,

726
00:27:32,079 --> 00:27:33,799
[SPEAKER_00] a Marulić je

727
00:27:33,799 --> 00:27:34,819
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom trenutku

728
00:27:34,819 --> 00:27:35,819
[SPEAKER_00] zaista, mislim,

729
00:27:35,819 --> 00:27:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] došao u nekakav

730
00:27:37,420 --> 00:27:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] popis fakultativnih autora,

731
00:27:39,420 --> 00:27:40,299
[SPEAKER_00] tako nekako.

732
00:27:40,299 --> 00:27:42,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nemam, dakle,

733
00:27:42,839 --> 00:27:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] nikakve dvojbe

734
00:27:44,079 --> 00:27:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] oko toga da Marulić

735
00:27:45,240 --> 00:27:46,660
[SPEAKER_00] kao klasik

736
00:27:46,660 --> 00:27:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] i kao,

737
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] ako hožete,

738
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] kanonski pisac

739
00:27:48,940 --> 00:27:50,140
[SPEAKER_00] treba biti u lektir.

740
00:27:50,140 --> 00:27:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] I pitanje je

741
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] što, koliko, kako.

742
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] I tu mislim da se

743
00:27:55,500 --> 00:27:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] nije još uvijek

744
00:27:56,900 --> 00:27:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] našao pravi ključ

745
00:27:57,980 --> 00:27:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim da

746
00:27:59,559 --> 00:28:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] čak ni srednjoškolcu

747
00:28:01,119 --> 00:28:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] ne treba

748
00:28:02,039 --> 00:28:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] nametati da čita,

749
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] recimo,

750
00:28:04,420 --> 00:28:05,799
[SPEAKER_00] Juditu u cijelosti.

751
00:28:05,799 --> 00:28:07,279
[SPEAKER_00] On to neće moći

752
00:28:07,279 --> 00:28:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] napraviti,

753
00:28:07,859 --> 00:28:08,940
[SPEAKER_00] za njega će to

754
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] biti nejasan zadatak

755
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:11,720
[SPEAKER_00] koji će mu izazvati

756
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,319
[SPEAKER_00] odbovinost.

757
00:28:12,319 --> 00:28:13,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mu kažete

758
00:28:13,799 --> 00:28:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] da čita Juditu

759
00:28:15,119 --> 00:28:15,660
[SPEAKER_00] u prijevodu

760
00:28:15,660 --> 00:28:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] na suremeni jezik,

761
00:28:16,599 --> 00:28:18,140
[SPEAKER_00] onda ste izgubili Marulić.

762
00:28:18,140 --> 00:28:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] Prijevod može biti

763
00:28:19,539 --> 00:28:20,359
[SPEAKER_00] pomošno sredstvo,

764
00:28:20,359 --> 00:28:22,660
[SPEAKER_00] ali u mojem gledanju

765
00:28:22,660 --> 00:28:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo opasno.

766
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:26,160
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da Marulića treba,

767
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] a to je zahtjevo ozbiljan

768
00:28:28,079 --> 00:28:29,339
[SPEAKER_00] i zadatak za profesora,

769
00:28:29,339 --> 00:28:30,259
[SPEAKER_00] ne je jednostavan,

770
00:28:30,259 --> 00:28:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] Marulića treba predoćiti

771
00:28:32,119 --> 00:28:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] ovog hrvatskog Marulića,

772
00:28:33,619 --> 00:28:34,720
[SPEAKER_00] Juditu, ako hoćete,

773
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:37,180
[SPEAKER_00] u odabranim ulomcima,

774
00:28:37,180 --> 00:28:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] dobro komentiranima

775
00:28:39,039 --> 00:28:40,160
[SPEAKER_00] i dobro objašnjenima.

776
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] Treba prije svega reći

777
00:28:42,059 --> 00:28:42,859
[SPEAKER_00] ovo što smo rekli,

778
00:28:42,859 --> 00:28:44,140
[SPEAKER_00] da pojam književnosti

779
00:28:44,140 --> 00:28:45,299
[SPEAKER_00] onda i sada nije isti.

780
00:28:45,299 --> 00:28:46,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da vi čitate,

781
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] naravno,

782
00:28:48,519 --> 00:28:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] biblijsku knjigu

783
00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:49,680
[SPEAKER_00] o Juditi,

784
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:50,740
[SPEAKER_00] ali prerađenu

785
00:28:50,740 --> 00:28:51,680
[SPEAKER_00] u pjesnički oblik.

786
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je prerađeno

787
00:28:52,900 --> 00:28:53,720
[SPEAKER_00] u pjesnički oblik,

788
00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:55,359
[SPEAKER_00] jedan dio tog pjesničkog oblika,

789
00:28:55,359 --> 00:28:57,019
[SPEAKER_00] ključni možda dio je jezik.

790
00:28:57,019 --> 00:28:58,819
[SPEAKER_00] Taj stari jezik,

791
00:28:58,819 --> 00:29:00,299
[SPEAKER_00] ta komplicirana forma.

792
00:29:00,299 --> 00:29:03,180
[SPEAKER_00] Uzmite 20 stihova,

793
00:29:03,180 --> 00:29:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] izvadite nepoznate riječi,

794
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] kao što ih izvadite

795
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] kad uđite engleski

796
00:29:06,940 --> 00:29:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] ili njemački

797
00:29:07,559 --> 00:29:08,220
[SPEAKER_00] ili latinski,

798
00:29:09,299 --> 00:29:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda pomalo složite to.

799
00:29:11,380 --> 00:29:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] Neće vam tu prijevod pomoći,

800
00:29:12,940 --> 00:29:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] nećete doći do kvalitete

801
00:29:15,380 --> 00:29:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] umjetničke,

802
00:29:15,980 --> 00:29:17,859
[SPEAKER_00] čitavući prijevodna suran jezika.

803
00:29:17,859 --> 00:29:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovako,

804
00:29:19,079 --> 00:29:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] sa pripremom,

805
00:29:19,900 --> 00:29:22,339
[SPEAKER_00] još ako netko može to pročitati

806
00:29:22,339 --> 00:29:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] onako kako treba,

807
00:29:24,119 --> 00:29:25,640
[SPEAKER_00] što je ozbiljan zadatak

808
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] sa maruličnim naglasima

809
00:29:27,380 --> 00:29:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] ili barem onim što mi znamo,

810
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:30,339
[SPEAKER_00] da bi trebalo zvučati,

811
00:29:30,339 --> 00:29:32,140
[SPEAKER_00] onda to postaje

812
00:29:32,140 --> 00:29:33,579
[SPEAKER_00] zvukovni doključaj.

813
00:29:33,579 --> 00:29:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] Onda možete govoriti

814
00:29:34,480 --> 00:29:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] i ne morate razumijeti,

815
00:29:35,420 --> 00:29:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] samo slušajte glasbu jezika.

816
00:29:37,099 --> 00:29:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zvukovost.

817
00:29:38,119 --> 00:29:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

818
00:29:38,559 --> 00:29:40,279
[SPEAKER_00] I to je prvi korak.

819
00:29:40,279 --> 00:29:41,799
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je to put

820
00:29:41,799 --> 00:29:42,640
[SPEAKER_00] kojim treba ići.

821
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] Taj put je zahtjevan,

822
00:29:44,539 --> 00:29:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] ali pedagogija je inače

823
00:29:47,079 --> 00:29:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] zahtjevna struka.

824
00:29:48,180 --> 00:29:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se profesorima divim.

825
00:29:50,119 --> 00:29:53,200
[SPEAKER_00] Izvrsni profesori su čudo u svijetu.

826
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ne?

827
00:29:53,940 --> 00:29:56,400
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo u srednjoj kozmetičkoj školi

828
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:57,759
[SPEAKER_01] odabrat odlomak

829
00:29:57,759 --> 00:29:58,819
[SPEAKER_01] gdje Marujić opisuje

830
00:29:58,819 --> 00:29:59,539
[SPEAKER_01] kako je se izdita resi.

831
00:29:59,539 --> 00:30:01,720
[SPEAKER_00] Molim lijepo kako je se izdita resi.

832
00:30:01,720 --> 00:30:03,440
[SPEAKER_00] Od deset biblijskih verseta

833
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:05,519
[SPEAKER_00] na prve 30 virtuoznih stihova.

834
00:30:05,519 --> 00:30:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] Koji zvone,

835
00:30:06,940 --> 00:30:08,359
[SPEAKER_00] zaista krasno.

836
00:30:08,359 --> 00:30:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] Za nekog za ko se govorilo

837
00:30:10,940 --> 00:30:11,779
[SPEAKER_01] da je bio sklon

838
00:30:11,779 --> 00:30:13,640
[SPEAKER_01] eremitaju povučenosti

839
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:14,259
[SPEAKER_01] nekakvom,

840
00:30:14,259 --> 00:30:16,920
[SPEAKER_01] a gotovo monaškom životu,

841
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:18,400
[SPEAKER_01] zanimava perspektiva

842
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:18,819
[SPEAKER_01] na ženu,

843
00:30:18,819 --> 00:30:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] na ženskosti,

844
00:30:19,579 --> 00:30:20,440
[SPEAKER_01] na žensku ljepotu.

845
00:30:20,440 --> 00:30:21,059
[SPEAKER_01] Da naravno,

846
00:30:21,059 --> 00:30:22,359
[SPEAKER_01] sad se ovdje šalim,

847
00:30:22,359 --> 00:30:23,660
[SPEAKER_01] jer čitajući druge

848
00:30:23,660 --> 00:30:24,440
[SPEAKER_01] Marujićeva djela

849
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,440
[SPEAKER_01] jako dobro znamo

850
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:26,500
[SPEAKER_01] njegovu renesansnost,

851
00:30:26,500 --> 00:30:27,720
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno njegovu

852
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:28,779
[SPEAKER_01] kreativnu umjetničku

853
00:30:28,779 --> 00:30:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] sposobnost da doživi,

854
00:30:31,579 --> 00:30:32,400
[SPEAKER_01] čak i ljepotu

855
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] u smislu...

856
00:30:33,619 --> 00:30:34,579
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je,

857
00:30:34,579 --> 00:30:35,200
[SPEAKER_00] tako je,

858
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] tako je.

859
00:30:35,539 --> 00:30:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] Mene ljepotu

860
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] na raznim područjima,

861
00:30:38,500 --> 00:30:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo u literaturi,

862
00:30:39,519 --> 00:30:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] nego u arhitekturi

863
00:30:40,579 --> 00:30:42,700
[SPEAKER_00] i u likovnosti.

864
00:30:42,700 --> 00:30:44,160
[SPEAKER_00] Kažu da se i sam bavio

865
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,759
[SPEAKER_00] likovnim stvaranjem.

866
00:30:45,759 --> 00:30:48,240
[SPEAKER_00] A što se tiče žena,

867
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] nekako iz ovoga što vidimo,

868
00:30:50,619 --> 00:30:53,039
[SPEAKER_00] nisu baš dobro prošle.

869
00:30:53,039 --> 00:30:55,140
[SPEAKER_00] U instituciji su

870
00:30:55,140 --> 00:30:58,420
[SPEAKER_00] puno manje zastupljene

871
00:30:58,420 --> 00:30:59,660
[SPEAKER_00] u broju primjera od muškarca.

872
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] Čak ima podjela muški primjeri,

873
00:31:01,980 --> 00:31:02,880
[SPEAKER_01] muškima ženski primjeri...

874
00:31:02,880 --> 00:31:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, uvijek su podjeljeni.

875
00:31:04,220 --> 00:31:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] U istom poglavlju

876
00:31:05,059 --> 00:31:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] imate uvijek prvo muške primjere,

877
00:31:06,460 --> 00:31:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] onda onda dade neki kratki prijaz,

878
00:31:08,079 --> 00:31:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] nemojmo zaboraviti ni,

879
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] recimo, ženski spol

880
00:31:12,559 --> 00:31:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] ili nemojmo da muškarci misle

881
00:31:14,500 --> 00:31:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] da su oni jedini, kreposni,

882
00:31:15,980 --> 00:31:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćemo uvesti nekoliko primjera žena.

883
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:20,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ali tih nekoliko primjera je manje od pola.

884
00:31:20,619 --> 00:31:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] Imaju dva poglavlja

885
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] koja su zasebno muški primjeri

886
00:31:24,220 --> 00:31:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] i posebno poglavlje ženski primjeri.

887
00:31:26,119 --> 00:31:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] To su jedina dva gdje su žene dobile

888
00:31:28,039 --> 00:31:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] zasebno poglavlje.

889
00:31:29,460 --> 00:31:31,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u ovim drugim dijelima,

890
00:31:31,700 --> 00:31:34,359
[SPEAKER_00] osim ljubavnih pjesama koje izuzimamo

891
00:31:34,359 --> 00:31:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] jer ima i takvih,

892
00:31:36,059 --> 00:31:38,259
[SPEAKER_00] u ovim drugima Maruliš se pomalo,

893
00:31:38,259 --> 00:31:39,640
[SPEAKER_00] možemo čak reći,

894
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] mizoginski postavio.

895
00:31:41,079 --> 00:31:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjeku kojeg kinji njegova žena

896
00:31:44,779 --> 00:31:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] pa ne zna kako on je pobjeći

897
00:31:47,119 --> 00:31:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] uopet u ovom tumaču starih nadpisa

898
00:31:49,500 --> 00:31:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] gdje strašno oštro napada žene

899
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] da su jezičave

900
00:31:53,019 --> 00:31:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] i da im se ne možeš nikako

901
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:57,839
[SPEAKER_00] riješiti te njihove govorljivosti.

902
00:31:58,500 --> 00:32:02,019
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ali opet u svom glavnom epu,

903
00:32:02,019 --> 00:32:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] možda najmjerodavnijem,

904
00:32:04,460 --> 00:32:06,920
[SPEAKER_01] neki kažu najuspjelijem dijelu Maruličeva,

905
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:08,359
[SPEAKER_01] iako je to nezahvalno na taj način,

906
00:32:08,359 --> 00:32:10,640
[SPEAKER_01] uspoređati, govoriti recimo da je Judita veća

907
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:12,279
[SPEAKER_01] od Avidiade ili od institucija.

908
00:32:12,279 --> 00:32:13,519
[SPEAKER_01] To i nema smisla.

909
00:32:13,519 --> 00:32:14,920
[SPEAKER_01] Nema smisla da bače.

910
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] Heroina je Judita.

911
00:32:16,079 --> 00:32:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] Točno.

912
00:32:17,039 --> 00:32:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] I to je još jedan od paradoksa

913
00:32:19,539 --> 00:32:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] s kojima se stalno susrećete

914
00:32:21,599 --> 00:32:23,180
[SPEAKER_00] kad se bavite Maruličem

915
00:32:23,180 --> 00:32:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] i to je možda najljepše i najpoticajnije.

916
00:32:26,599 --> 00:32:28,799
[SPEAKER_00] Judita je ženski epski juna.

917
00:32:28,799 --> 00:32:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je u evropskoj književnosti

918
00:32:31,539 --> 00:32:32,900
[SPEAKER_00] i renesanse nečuveno.

919
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,700
[SPEAKER_00] Nečuveno je već i to

920
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:36,700
[SPEAKER_00] da je starozavjetni lik

921
00:32:36,700 --> 00:32:38,279
[SPEAKER_00] uzet za junaka.

922
00:32:39,019 --> 00:32:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] Humanistički pjesnici njegova doba

923
00:32:41,539 --> 00:32:43,700
[SPEAKER_00] uzimaju novi zavjet kao temu

924
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:46,720
[SPEAKER_00] i obično je Krist glavni junak

925
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:50,200
[SPEAKER_00] ili je tu negdje oko novozavjetnih tema

926
00:32:50,200 --> 00:32:51,299
[SPEAKER_00] se sve vrti.

927
00:32:51,299 --> 00:32:53,779
[SPEAKER_00] Stari zavjet u to vrijeme nije bio

928
00:32:53,779 --> 00:32:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] tako atraktivan.

929
00:32:55,380 --> 00:32:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] A evo Marulič uzima dva starozavjetna lika

930
00:32:57,920 --> 00:32:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] u latinskom epku Davida,

931
00:32:59,279 --> 00:33:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] a u hrvatskom Juditu,

932
00:33:01,380 --> 00:33:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] dakle starozavjetnu, žensku,

933
00:33:03,079 --> 00:33:05,779
[SPEAKER_00] i još osob oko koje

934
00:33:05,779 --> 00:33:07,700
[SPEAKER_00] crkveni cenzori imaju

935
00:33:07,700 --> 00:33:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] ozbiljnih primjeti.

936
00:33:09,019 --> 00:33:12,259
[SPEAKER_01] Vezano za crkvenu cenzuru

937
00:33:12,259 --> 00:33:13,539
[SPEAKER_01] možemo se nakratko stvarniti

938
00:33:13,539 --> 00:33:14,740
[SPEAKER_01] na sudbinu jedne knjige,

939
00:33:14,740 --> 00:33:16,140
[SPEAKER_01] iako je to naslov jednog

940
00:33:16,140 --> 00:33:17,799
[SPEAKER_01] francuskog a vrhovnskog Maruljega

941
00:33:17,799 --> 00:33:18,880
[SPEAKER_01] koji se odnosi na jednu drugu

942
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:19,640
[SPEAKER_01] Maruličevo dijelo,

943
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:20,599
[SPEAKER_01] ali sudbina jedne knjige

944
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:21,759
[SPEAKER_01] može postođati kao

945
00:33:21,759 --> 00:33:23,240
[SPEAKER_01] u skladu s onom

946
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:25,019
[SPEAKER_01] da svaka knjiga ima svoju sudbinu

947
00:33:25,019 --> 00:33:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] s institucijom.

948
00:33:26,079 --> 00:33:26,900
[SPEAKER_01] Na ima, to je knjiga

949
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:27,839
[SPEAKER_01] koja je doživjela

950
00:33:27,839 --> 00:33:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] pustolovinu pravu

951
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,220
[SPEAKER_01] od činjenice da je

952
00:33:30,220 --> 00:33:32,740
[SPEAKER_01] najuspjelije jedini hrvatski pravi bestseller,

953
00:33:32,740 --> 00:33:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] da je Marulič kao zavičani pisac

954
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,740
[SPEAKER_01] koji se previše nije micao,

955
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:38,140
[SPEAKER_01] njegov dijapazom šetanja

956
00:33:38,140 --> 00:33:40,160
[SPEAKER_01] je bio od Solina do Šolte.

957
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:40,900
[SPEAKER_01] Do Venecije?

958
00:33:40,900 --> 00:33:43,200
[SPEAKER_01] I do Venecije, da, definitivno.

959
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:45,140
[SPEAKER_01] I je na posjetku,

960
00:33:45,140 --> 00:33:46,740
[SPEAKER_01] zahvaljujući juditi,

961
00:33:46,740 --> 00:33:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] dospio i do Japana,

962
00:33:48,380 --> 00:33:50,559
[SPEAKER_01] do Portugala, Češke,

963
00:33:50,559 --> 00:33:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] cijele Njemačke i tako dalje.

964
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, proput ovo je sve.

965
00:33:54,079 --> 00:33:55,359
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, od činjenice

966
00:33:55,359 --> 00:33:56,400
[SPEAKER_01] koje je nadahnjivala,

967
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] knjige koje je nadahnjivala svece,

968
00:33:58,599 --> 00:33:59,400
[SPEAKER_01] došlo se i do toga

969
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:00,359
[SPEAKER_01] da ta knjiga skupa

970
00:34:00,359 --> 00:34:02,559
[SPEAKER_01] s makijavijavim dijelima

971
00:34:02,559 --> 00:34:03,740
[SPEAKER_01] bude spaljena.

972
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:06,339
[SPEAKER_00] u Sijeni 1564.

973
00:34:06,339 --> 00:34:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] Srećom imamo taj arhivski podatak.

974
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znamo zašto je

975
00:34:11,079 --> 00:34:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] cenzura u Sijeni

976
00:34:13,159 --> 00:34:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] spaljila instituciju.

977
00:34:15,119 --> 00:34:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] Taj podatak nije sačuvan,

978
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] ali očito je nešto

979
00:34:18,840 --> 00:34:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] doktrinarno u njoj smetalo.

980
00:34:21,059 --> 00:34:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] Možda isto ono što je

981
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] institucija dovela na indeks

982
00:34:24,460 --> 00:34:27,059
[SPEAKER_00] zabranjenih knjiga 1612.

983
00:34:27,059 --> 00:34:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] A to mjesto koje je žuljalo

984
00:34:31,460 --> 00:34:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] cenzorske čitaceđe

985
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:35,219
[SPEAKER_00] upravo ono mjesto

986
00:34:35,219 --> 00:34:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] u koje je Judita

987
00:34:36,539 --> 00:34:38,860
[SPEAKER_00] važan argumentacijski sastojak,

988
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] to je Marulićevo poglavlje

989
00:34:41,079 --> 00:34:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] četvrta knjiga institucije

990
00:34:44,500 --> 00:34:47,679
[SPEAKER_00] o tome je li laž dopuštena ili nije.

991
00:34:47,679 --> 00:34:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] I tu Marulić daje jedan odgovor koji se nije svidio

992
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] cenzorima.

993
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže, laže naravno grijeh i to težak grijeh,

994
00:34:57,519 --> 00:34:59,280
[SPEAKER_00] ali laž je ipak u nekim

995
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] specijalnim slučajima dopuštena.

996
00:35:01,199 --> 00:35:03,739
[SPEAKER_00] Onda naime, on to vrlo jasno kaže,

997
00:35:03,739 --> 00:35:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] kada bi se govoreći istinu

998
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,679
[SPEAKER_00] počinila veća šteta

999
00:35:07,679 --> 00:35:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] ili počinio veći grijeh,

1000
00:35:09,179 --> 00:35:11,320
[SPEAKER_00] nego kad se za ta istina

1001
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] ili laže.

1002
00:35:12,179 --> 00:35:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] I kao primjer, jedan od niza primjera

1003
00:35:14,800 --> 00:35:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] svetopisamskih primjera

1004
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] navodi Juditu.

1005
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] Judita je lagala holofernu

1006
00:35:22,099 --> 00:35:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] za to da bi spasila

1007
00:35:24,579 --> 00:35:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] svoj grad, svoj narod,

1008
00:35:26,599 --> 00:35:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] sebe samu, dakle, svoju vjeru.

1009
00:35:29,159 --> 00:35:31,300
[SPEAKER_00] I to je po Maruliću

1010
00:35:31,300 --> 00:35:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] dopuštena laž.

1011
00:35:32,940 --> 00:35:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] Cenzori se nisu s tim ne slagali,

1012
00:35:34,699 --> 00:35:37,219
[SPEAKER_00] tražili su, ne da se cijela institucija zabrani,

1013
00:35:37,219 --> 00:35:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] nego je stavljen u takozvani drugi razred

1014
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:42,099
[SPEAKER_00] da se mora pročistiti.

1015
00:35:42,179 --> 00:35:43,139
[SPEAKER_00] Od odrađenima uvjetima.

1016
00:35:43,139 --> 00:35:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] Odrađenima, dakle, što znači pročistiti,

1017
00:35:45,460 --> 00:35:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] to je vrlo, u praktičnom smislu,

1018
00:35:47,860 --> 00:35:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo nezahvalan zadatak.

1019
00:35:49,559 --> 00:35:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, treba uzeti svake primjera knjige

1020
00:35:51,460 --> 00:35:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] do kojeg možete doći

1021
00:35:52,739 --> 00:35:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] i onda su ljudi za to zaduženi.

1022
00:35:55,059 --> 00:35:56,679
[SPEAKER_00] Po uputi, to je,

1023
00:35:56,679 --> 00:35:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] iz tog poglavlja, od mjesta tog do tog,

1024
00:35:58,960 --> 00:36:01,179
[SPEAKER_00] morali su zamrčiti crnilom

1025
00:36:01,179 --> 00:36:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] te rečenice, te redke.

1026
00:36:02,699 --> 00:36:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] I zaista imate u Evropskim knjižnicama

1027
00:36:05,079 --> 00:36:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] primjerke institucije gdje su

1028
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] neka mjesta koja je tražila cenzura

1029
00:36:09,059 --> 00:36:11,099
[SPEAKER_00] rukom zamrčena, drugačije nije išla.

1030
00:36:11,099 --> 00:36:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da, i u nekom drugom dijelu,

1031
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:14,099
[SPEAKER_01] ako se ne veram u dialogu o Herkulu,

1032
00:36:14,099 --> 00:36:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] njegova posveta je razmu, isto tako je neka...

1033
00:36:16,099 --> 00:36:18,760
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, posveta je razmu koja se nije nekome svidjela,

1034
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] jer je on silno nakvalio razma,

1035
00:36:20,619 --> 00:36:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] što je nama silno drago, naravno.

1036
00:36:22,420 --> 00:36:24,940
[SPEAKER_00] Imate istovremeno,

1037
00:36:24,940 --> 00:36:27,340
[SPEAKER_00] dok se to dešava u Sijeni,

1038
00:36:27,340 --> 00:36:28,900
[SPEAKER_00] jedan izlazi

1039
00:36:28,900 --> 00:36:30,599
[SPEAKER_00] taljanski prirod institucije,

1040
00:36:30,599 --> 00:36:32,239
[SPEAKER_00] koji je potpuno cijelovito,

1041
00:36:32,239 --> 00:36:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem nema nikakve...

1042
00:36:33,420 --> 00:36:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovog Sijeni je bila nekakva lokalna priča.

1043
00:36:36,260 --> 00:36:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] E sad,

1044
00:36:37,039 --> 00:36:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] indeks istišće 612.

1045
00:36:39,519 --> 00:36:41,239
[SPEAKER_00] je ipak obavezivao cijelu

1046
00:36:41,239 --> 00:36:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] zajednicu,

1047
00:36:42,579 --> 00:36:44,739
[SPEAKER_00] kršćansku ili čitatelsku ili kako hoće.

1048
00:36:44,739 --> 00:36:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] Da, možemo reći da su Maruliću zamjerali

1049
00:36:47,039 --> 00:36:49,360
[SPEAKER_01] antikantovsku poziciju po pitanju laži.

1050
00:36:49,360 --> 00:36:51,239
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ipak je u određenim situacijama

1051
00:36:51,239 --> 00:36:52,519
[SPEAKER_01] cilj opravdava sredstvo.

1052
00:36:52,519 --> 00:36:55,179
[SPEAKER_01] Tu je srodan makijavedio, šalim se.

1053
00:36:55,179 --> 00:36:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali tu vidite koliko je Marulić

1054
00:36:57,559 --> 00:37:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, nije uskrogudan mislilac.

1055
00:37:01,300 --> 00:37:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] On, naravno, zasniva te svoje stavove

1056
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo na čitanju Biblije,

1057
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:07,340
[SPEAKER_00] nego i na čitanju crkvenih otaca,

1058
00:37:07,340 --> 00:37:09,320
[SPEAKER_00] jer o tome je Sveti Augustin

1059
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] raspravljao, o tome je laž dopuštena

1060
00:37:11,420 --> 00:37:12,900
[SPEAKER_00] i nije. To je pitanje otvoreno.

1061
00:37:12,900 --> 00:37:14,579
[SPEAKER_00] Imat ćemo na sljedećem simpoziju

1062
00:37:14,579 --> 00:37:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] na Marulićem danima

1063
00:37:15,599 --> 00:37:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] jedno izlaganje koje opet otvara

1064
00:37:18,380 --> 00:37:20,719
[SPEAKER_00] tu temu, Marulić i pitanje laži.

1065
00:37:20,719 --> 00:37:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] Njegovi uzori,

1066
00:37:22,440 --> 00:37:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] recimo, ili predložci u tome pitanje.

1067
00:37:24,820 --> 00:37:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, i to je jedna od tema

1068
00:37:26,460 --> 00:37:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] koje se vraćamo.

1069
00:37:27,460 --> 00:37:30,500
[SPEAKER_01] Samorazumljivo je govoriti

1070
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:32,420
[SPEAKER_01] o Maruliću kao kršćanskom autoru.

1071
00:37:32,420 --> 00:37:34,800
[SPEAKER_01] Istaknuli smo u razgovoru

1072
00:37:34,800 --> 00:37:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] centralno mjesto Biblije,

1073
00:37:36,380 --> 00:37:38,739
[SPEAKER_01] Božje riječi i nabožnoj literaturi

1074
00:37:38,739 --> 00:37:40,239
[SPEAKER_01] koje on posvetio golemi dio

1075
00:37:40,239 --> 00:37:42,079
[SPEAKER_01] svog oposta na latinskom jeziku.

1076
00:37:42,079 --> 00:37:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali što nam možete reći o Maruliću

1077
00:37:43,960 --> 00:37:45,639
[SPEAKER_01] i anticije, o utjecajima

1078
00:37:45,639 --> 00:37:47,719
[SPEAKER_01] o takozvanom njegovom ambivalentnom

1079
00:37:47,719 --> 00:37:48,920
[SPEAKER_01] odnosu prema anticiji,

1080
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] grčkoj, rimskoj filozofiji, mitologiji,

1081
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] književnosti, bez koje ne bi smo mogli zamisliti njegovu.

1082
00:37:54,460 --> 00:37:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] pokušat ću u tri slike,

1083
00:37:58,079 --> 00:37:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] pa možemo eventualno dulje.

1084
00:37:59,960 --> 00:38:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] Prva slika je Marulić sa 15 ili 16 godina.

1085
00:38:03,119 --> 00:38:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mladi Marulić piše

1086
00:38:06,599 --> 00:38:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] Juriju Šižgoriću,

1087
00:38:08,599 --> 00:38:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] tada već uglednom pjesniku.

1088
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pišem u pismo u kojem ga uspoređuje sa,

1089
00:38:19,460 --> 00:38:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] doslovno citiram,

1090
00:38:21,159 --> 00:38:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] onim drevnim i svetim pjesnicima,

1091
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] a pod njima misli rimske pjesnike,

1092
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] konkretno ljubavne legičare,

1093
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] Propersija, Tibula i Ovidija.

1094
00:38:32,260 --> 00:38:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, za njega su ti poganski autori,

1095
00:38:35,119 --> 00:38:35,920
[SPEAKER_00] da tako kažemo,

1096
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] oni drevni i sveti pjesnici.

1097
00:38:38,500 --> 00:38:39,679
[SPEAKER_00] To je Marulić sa 16 godina.

1098
00:38:39,679 --> 00:38:42,780
[SPEAKER_00] Marulić sa 69 ili 70 godina

1099
00:38:42,780 --> 00:38:45,219
[SPEAKER_00] piše onu posvetu Tomi Nigeru,

1100
00:38:45,219 --> 00:38:46,360
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj hvali je Razma,

1101
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže

1102
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] kako danas možemo se diviti

1103
00:38:53,199 --> 00:38:54,280
[SPEAKER_00] o štromnosti zaključivanja

1104
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:57,239
[SPEAKER_00] naših teoretičara, teologa,

1105
00:38:57,239 --> 00:38:59,800
[SPEAKER_00] ali tko god je suživanjem čitao

1106
00:38:59,800 --> 00:39:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] antičke pisce,

1107
00:39:00,860 --> 00:39:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] ne može ne primijetiti

1108
00:39:02,579 --> 00:39:04,320
[SPEAKER_00] da su ovi današnji dosadni.

1109
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] I treba se nadati

1110
00:39:06,500 --> 00:39:09,219
[SPEAKER_00] da će, kao što je Razma obnovio

1111
00:39:09,219 --> 00:39:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] sjajnu literarnost,

1112
00:39:12,159 --> 00:39:15,420
[SPEAKER_00] stilistične kvalitete pisanja,

1113
00:39:16,139 --> 00:39:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] da će opet biti takvih ljudi,

1114
00:39:17,619 --> 00:39:18,679
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, koji će biti

1115
00:39:18,679 --> 00:39:20,179
[SPEAKER_00] kao novi Jeronimi

1116
00:39:20,179 --> 00:39:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] ili novi Ambrozi,

1117
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] koji će opet znati

1118
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] crkveni nauk,

1119
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] izlagati izvrsnim književnim stilom.

1120
00:39:26,880 --> 00:39:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] To su dvije točke.

1121
00:39:28,639 --> 00:39:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] U sredini je Marulić zreli

1122
00:39:30,500 --> 00:39:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] sa 50 godina,

1123
00:39:31,860 --> 00:39:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] kada piše

1124
00:39:32,780 --> 00:39:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] na njegovom radnom stolu institucija.

1125
00:39:34,880 --> 00:39:37,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je došljena negdje 1499.

1126
00:39:37,860 --> 00:39:40,059
[SPEAKER_00] Negdje u to vrijeme

1127
00:39:40,059 --> 00:39:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] ili nekoliko godina nakon toga

1128
00:39:41,639 --> 00:39:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] Marulić ima na svom stolu

1129
00:39:43,059 --> 00:39:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] ili možda na drugom stolu,

1130
00:39:44,260 --> 00:39:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] ako hoćete,

1131
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] ima rukopis

1132
00:39:46,599 --> 00:39:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] Petronijeva satirikona,

1133
00:39:48,099 --> 00:39:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, jednog dijela

1134
00:39:49,539 --> 00:39:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] iz rimske književnosti

1135
00:39:50,519 --> 00:39:52,019
[SPEAKER_00] koje nikako ne možete povezati

1136
00:39:52,019 --> 00:39:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] sa bilo kakvim čudorežem

1137
00:39:53,559 --> 00:39:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] ili sa čakav ovoštvo

1138
00:39:55,300 --> 00:39:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] antičkom smislu,

1139
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] moralnom povukom,

1140
00:39:57,539 --> 00:39:58,659
[SPEAKER_00] egzemplarnovćom.

1141
00:39:58,659 --> 00:40:00,320
[SPEAKER_00] Taj rukopis ima

1142
00:40:00,320 --> 00:40:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo Petronijev satirikon,

1143
00:40:02,239 --> 00:40:03,219
[SPEAKER_00] nego ima u dodatku

1144
00:40:03,219 --> 00:40:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] katulove pjesme.

1145
00:40:04,139 --> 00:40:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] Katul je pjesnik ljubavnih pjesama,

1146
00:40:06,119 --> 00:40:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] poznat po tome,

1147
00:40:06,980 --> 00:40:07,679
[SPEAKER_00] među ostalim,

1148
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] što također se zna izražavati

1149
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:11,900
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo plastičnim, da tako kažemo,

1150
00:40:11,900 --> 00:40:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] jezikom, dakle bez zadrške,

1151
00:40:13,940 --> 00:40:15,780
[SPEAKER_00] kad je riječ i o spolnosti

1152
00:40:15,780 --> 00:40:17,320
[SPEAKER_00] i o međuljudskim odnosima

1153
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] i o uvrijedanju, ako hoćete.

1154
00:40:19,260 --> 00:40:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] Marulić čita te pjesme u rukopisu

1155
00:40:22,699 --> 00:40:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] i piše svoje sažetke na marginama

1156
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] i svoje male komentare

1157
00:40:27,460 --> 00:40:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] i prepisuje neke od ovih

1158
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:33,780
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo, kako bih rekao,

1159
00:40:33,780 --> 00:40:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] neugodnih izraza svom rukom.

1160
00:40:36,039 --> 00:40:37,179
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1161
00:40:37,179 --> 00:40:40,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što su mu zanimljivi jezično,

1162
00:40:40,820 --> 00:40:42,340
[SPEAKER_00] zato što u tom trenutku

1163
00:40:42,340 --> 00:40:43,820
[SPEAKER_00] filološki impuls

1164
00:40:43,820 --> 00:40:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] nadređen svakom drugom.

1165
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:47,340
[SPEAKER_00] On čita jednog izvrsnog

1166
00:40:47,340 --> 00:40:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] antičkog pjesnika,

1167
00:40:48,300 --> 00:40:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] sjajno uživa u tome očito,

1168
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:52,719
[SPEAKER_00] ispisuje sažetke pjesama,

1169
00:40:52,719 --> 00:40:54,500
[SPEAKER_00] ispisuje riječi koje nikad sam

1170
00:40:54,500 --> 00:40:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] neće koristiti u svojim dijelima.

1171
00:40:56,739 --> 00:40:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovdje su o njemu

1172
00:40:58,199 --> 00:40:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] one važne, nove, zanimljive.

1173
00:40:59,699 --> 00:41:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da govori se i općenito

1174
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] o nekakvim predlošcima,

1175
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:04,400
[SPEAKER_01] ako ćemo govoriti o šinom smislu,

1176
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:05,980
[SPEAKER_01] Marulića u uzorima

1177
00:41:05,980 --> 00:41:06,920
[SPEAKER_01] kojima se on povodio

1178
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:08,559
[SPEAKER_01] pišući, recimo, institucija,

1179
00:41:08,559 --> 00:41:10,280
[SPEAKER_01] u pozadinima Marka Valerija.

1180
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ima Valerija Maksima, da,

1181
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] koji piše zbirku

1182
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] primernih figura iz antike,

1183
00:41:17,039 --> 00:41:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] iz grčkog i rimskog svijeta

1184
00:41:18,619 --> 00:41:20,920
[SPEAKER_00] i Marulić je on uzor.

1185
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:24,320
[SPEAKER_00] Na nekim mjestima imate uzore

1186
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:25,320
[SPEAKER_00] koji su skriveni.

1187
00:41:25,559 --> 00:41:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] kad piše starozavetne ličnosti,

1188
00:41:27,519 --> 00:41:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] jedno dijelo koje nije baš jako

1189
00:41:30,019 --> 00:41:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] zanimljivo za čitanje,

1190
00:41:32,099 --> 00:41:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] to je sažetak starog zavjeta,

1191
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali ozbiljnim filološkim čitanjem

1192
00:41:37,099 --> 00:41:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] se odskrilo su se tragovi

1193
00:41:39,019 --> 00:41:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] poznavanja načela antičke biografije,

1194
00:41:42,579 --> 00:41:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] koja su onda primjenjena na biblijsku građu.

1195
00:41:45,059 --> 00:41:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne govorimo o latinskim pjesmama,

1196
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira na njihov sadržaj,

1197
00:41:49,460 --> 00:41:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] ako hoćete, i one koje su nabožnog karaktera,

1198
00:41:52,579 --> 00:41:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] one neminovno odaju

1199
00:41:54,980 --> 00:41:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] izvrsno poznavanje klasika,

1200
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,400
[SPEAKER_00] rimskih pjesmika u prvom redu.

1201
00:41:59,059 --> 00:42:01,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna od antolozijskih pjesama Maruličevih,

1202
00:42:01,139 --> 00:42:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] ne za Maruličev opis,

1203
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:04,719
[SPEAKER_00] nego uvjeren sam za evropski humanizam,

1204
00:42:04,719 --> 00:42:07,320
[SPEAKER_00] je Himan Bogu u heksametrima.

1205
00:42:07,320 --> 00:42:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] To je sjajna pjesma.

1206
00:42:08,619 --> 00:42:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] To je neobično lijepa pjesma,

1207
00:42:10,800 --> 00:42:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] koja je prožeta,

1208
00:42:12,519 --> 00:42:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] to se ne da čak ni točno,

1209
00:42:14,679 --> 00:42:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] znate, definirati,

1210
00:42:15,659 --> 00:42:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali prožela je nekakvim lukrecijevskim duhom.

1211
00:42:18,019 --> 00:42:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ste čitali lukrecija,

1212
00:42:19,440 --> 00:42:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] neminovno morate čitajući tu pjesmu

1213
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] pomisliti na to kako je Bog stvorio prirodu,

1214
00:42:24,960 --> 00:42:26,739
[SPEAKER_00] kako ta priroda izgleda,

1215
00:42:26,739 --> 00:42:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] kako živi, kako je njezino bogatstvo.

1216
00:42:28,699 --> 00:42:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto što se možda ne odražava

1217
00:42:30,880 --> 00:42:32,860
[SPEAKER_00] u nekoj detekciji,

1218
00:42:32,860 --> 00:42:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] reminiscencija konkretnih pjesmičkih,

1219
00:42:35,420 --> 00:42:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] ali u duhu jest.

1220
00:42:36,400 --> 00:42:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] Time Maruliče dolazi u svezu,

1221
00:42:39,539 --> 00:42:40,659
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, preko lukrecija

1222
00:42:40,659 --> 00:42:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] i sa grčkom, antičkom filozofijom,

1223
00:42:43,019 --> 00:42:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] sa pikurom i tako dalje.

1224
00:42:44,340 --> 00:42:46,780
[SPEAKER_01] Iako je, ćeo već u evanđeli starona,

1225
00:42:46,860 --> 00:42:49,119
[SPEAKER_01] tragove, afirmativno govore

1226
00:42:49,119 --> 00:42:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] o stojičkoj etike.

1227
00:42:49,960 --> 00:42:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] O stojičkoj, tako.

1228
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:52,179
[SPEAKER_01] Srodnost stojičke etike,

1229
00:42:52,179 --> 00:42:54,019
[SPEAKER_01] evanđelja, evanđeljske etike,

1230
00:42:54,019 --> 00:42:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] morala, parelele,

1231
00:42:56,119 --> 00:42:57,599
[SPEAKER_01] Seneca, Pavao i opće mjesto.

1232
00:42:57,599 --> 00:42:58,320
[SPEAKER_01] Kao tako.

1233
00:42:58,320 --> 00:43:00,599
[SPEAKER_01] Što nam možete reći

1234
00:43:00,599 --> 00:43:02,639
[SPEAKER_01] o međunarodnoj recepciji Maruličevoj?

1235
00:43:02,639 --> 00:43:04,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je postojala

1236
00:43:04,639 --> 00:43:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] u 16. i 17. stoljeću.

1237
00:43:06,519 --> 00:43:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] Bila je, dakle, počela je već

1238
00:43:08,559 --> 00:43:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] za njegova života.

1239
00:43:09,440 --> 00:43:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] Mi, najkraće to možemo reći,

1240
00:43:12,980 --> 00:43:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] možda u brojkama,

1241
00:43:13,760 --> 00:43:15,679
[SPEAKER_00] tri dijela institucije evanđeli star

1242
00:43:15,679 --> 00:43:18,219
[SPEAKER_00] i 50 priča su u ta dva stoljeća

1243
00:43:18,219 --> 00:43:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] objavljeni oko 80 puta

1244
00:43:20,059 --> 00:43:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] u izvorniku u priodima

1245
00:43:22,079 --> 00:43:23,340
[SPEAKER_00] na niz jezika,

1246
00:43:23,340 --> 00:43:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] sve važne evropske jezike,

1247
00:43:24,699 --> 00:43:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] možemo reći.

1248
00:43:25,380 --> 00:43:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ako biste uzeli i pjesmu

1249
00:43:27,619 --> 00:43:28,179
[SPEAKER_00] o Povuci,

1250
00:43:28,179 --> 00:43:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] Maruličevoj,

1251
00:43:29,079 --> 00:43:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] pjesmu o Povuci

1252
00:43:29,800 --> 00:43:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] gospodina našeg Isusa Krista

1253
00:43:31,480 --> 00:43:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] koji visi na križu,

1254
00:43:32,480 --> 00:43:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] onda se taj broj diže

1255
00:43:34,320 --> 00:43:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] do dvije stotine.

1256
00:43:36,079 --> 00:43:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] samo što pjesma nije objavljena

1257
00:43:37,360 --> 00:43:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] samostalno,

1258
00:43:38,019 --> 00:43:40,179
[SPEAKER_00] nego u sklopu jednog drugog dijela

1259
00:43:40,179 --> 00:43:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] koja je imala široku distribuciju.

1260
00:43:41,980 --> 00:43:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga 18. stoljeće

1261
00:43:45,079 --> 00:43:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] prosvjetitelstvo ima smisla za Maruliča

1262
00:43:48,119 --> 00:43:49,739
[SPEAKER_00] kao pista povijesnih spisa.

1263
00:43:49,739 --> 00:43:52,260
[SPEAKER_00] A ova moralno-teološka dijela

1264
00:43:52,260 --> 00:43:54,860
[SPEAKER_00] padaju manje više u zakora.

1265
00:43:54,860 --> 00:43:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] U 19. stoljeće je otkriva Maruliča

1266
00:43:57,460 --> 00:43:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] kao našeg,

1267
00:43:58,699 --> 00:43:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] kao hrvatskog,

1268
00:43:59,420 --> 00:44:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] sa buđenjem nacionalnih svijesti

1269
00:44:01,300 --> 00:44:02,900
[SPEAKER_00] i nacionalnih institucija u Hrvatskoj.

1270
00:44:02,900 --> 00:44:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] Pojavio je se prvo izdanje

1271
00:44:04,179 --> 00:44:05,360
[SPEAKER_00] starih pisaca Hrvatskih.

1272
00:44:05,360 --> 00:44:05,860
[SPEAKER_00] Kuljević.

1273
00:44:05,860 --> 00:44:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda se pojavio je,

1274
00:44:07,719 --> 00:44:08,860
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, Kukuljević,

1275
00:44:08,860 --> 00:44:09,659
[SPEAKER_00] tako i Jagić,

1276
00:44:09,659 --> 00:44:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda se pomalo počinje

1277
00:44:11,920 --> 00:44:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] Maruličeva slava

1278
00:44:13,500 --> 00:44:16,719
[SPEAKER_00] dosta polagano mora se reći

1279
00:44:16,719 --> 00:44:19,320
[SPEAKER_00] sve do 70. godina 20. stoljeća

1280
00:44:19,320 --> 00:44:21,480
[SPEAKER_00] kada ona opet počinje rasti.

1281
00:44:21,480 --> 00:44:22,880
[SPEAKER_00] U današnje vrijeme

1282
00:44:22,880 --> 00:44:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] Marulič u neku ruku ponavlja

1283
00:44:25,880 --> 00:44:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] slavu 16. i 17. stoljeća,

1284
00:44:28,880 --> 00:44:30,760
[SPEAKER_00] ali opet pomalo paradoksalno,

1285
00:44:30,760 --> 00:44:32,860
[SPEAKER_00] ne više toliko latinskim dijelima

1286
00:44:32,860 --> 00:44:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] nego i Judito.

1287
00:44:33,619 --> 00:44:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] Judita je u zadnjih 30-40 godina

1288
00:44:37,340 --> 00:44:39,280
[SPEAKER_00] u cijelosti prevedena na pet

1289
00:44:39,280 --> 00:44:40,699
[SPEAKER_00] evropskih jezika

1290
00:44:40,699 --> 00:44:44,219
[SPEAKER_00] i u ulomcima još na dva jezika

1291
00:44:44,219 --> 00:44:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] i na Esperanto.

1292
00:44:45,159 --> 00:44:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ona je danas

1293
00:44:47,480 --> 00:44:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] u Evropi prisutna.

1294
00:44:49,019 --> 00:44:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] Uskoro će biti i Davidijada

1295
00:44:52,099 --> 00:44:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] jer očekujemo

1296
00:44:53,920 --> 00:44:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] u travni na Maruličevim danima

1297
00:44:56,340 --> 00:44:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] prvi engleski prijevod

1298
00:44:58,099 --> 00:44:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] cijelokupne Davidijade.

1299
00:44:59,980 --> 00:45:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] Na prvi ga je dan Amerikanac.

1300
00:45:02,260 --> 00:45:03,719
[SPEAKER_00] Izvrstvo.

1301
00:45:03,719 --> 00:45:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] Marulič i hrvatske književnice.

1302
00:45:07,019 --> 00:45:08,219
[SPEAKER_01] Jako kompleksna,

1303
00:45:08,219 --> 00:45:11,219
[SPEAKER_01] a i u neku ruku zanimljiva tema.

1304
00:45:11,340 --> 00:45:12,340
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje je u rukama imamo

1305
00:45:12,340 --> 00:45:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] zbornik,

1306
00:45:14,840 --> 00:45:17,739
[SPEAKER_01] 1950-1450 godina,

1307
00:45:17,739 --> 00:45:20,260
[SPEAKER_01] godina Maruličeva rođenja.

1308
00:45:20,260 --> 00:45:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj zbornik krije jednu onako

1309
00:45:22,119 --> 00:45:24,159
[SPEAKER_01] povijesnu književnu

1310
00:45:24,159 --> 00:45:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] zanimljivost ili kuriozitet.

1311
00:45:26,420 --> 00:45:27,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ja u rukama na ime imam

1312
00:45:27,579 --> 00:45:28,860
[SPEAKER_01] takozvani cenzurirani,

1313
00:45:28,860 --> 00:45:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno okrnjeni zbornik.

1314
00:45:30,260 --> 00:45:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] Kogo se i o le bavi

1315
00:45:31,420 --> 00:45:32,960
[SPEAKER_01] Maruličem i hrvatskom književnošću,

1316
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:34,360
[SPEAKER_01] kad ta će doći do podatka

1317
00:45:34,360 --> 00:45:36,760
[SPEAKER_01] da je u prvotnom izdanju

1318
00:45:36,760 --> 00:45:37,760
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje postao članak

1319
00:45:37,760 --> 00:45:38,719
[SPEAKER_01] posvećenu Maruliču

1320
00:45:38,719 --> 00:45:39,840
[SPEAKER_01] kojega možemo naći

1321
00:45:39,840 --> 00:45:40,780
[SPEAKER_01] u časopisima.

1322
00:45:40,780 --> 00:45:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

1323
00:45:41,260 --> 00:45:44,480
[SPEAKER_01] Profesora Vladimira Filipovića,

1324
00:45:44,480 --> 00:45:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] uglasovjetno-hrvatskog

1325
00:45:45,579 --> 00:45:47,440
[SPEAKER_01] profesora filozofije,

1326
00:45:47,440 --> 00:45:49,500
[SPEAKER_01] pisa jednog od važnijih

1327
00:45:49,500 --> 00:45:50,739
[SPEAKER_01] riješnika filozofskih.

1328
00:45:50,739 --> 00:45:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] Točno.

1329
00:45:51,260 --> 00:45:53,519
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno,

1330
00:45:53,519 --> 00:45:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] prije izrade ovoga zbornika

1331
00:45:55,400 --> 00:45:57,059
[SPEAKER_01] osjetio se duha autoritet

1332
00:45:57,059 --> 00:45:58,639
[SPEAKER_01] jednog isto tako istaknutog

1333
00:45:58,639 --> 00:46:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] velikana hrvatske književnosti,

1334
00:46:00,079 --> 00:46:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] to je Miroslav Krleš.

1335
00:46:01,800 --> 00:46:03,639
[SPEAKER_01] U svojoj panorami,

1336
00:46:03,940 --> 00:46:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, nekakvom izvatku

1337
00:46:05,619 --> 00:46:07,820
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se nalaze citati

1338
00:46:07,820 --> 00:46:09,059
[SPEAKER_01] raznoraznih

1339
00:46:09,059 --> 00:46:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] raznoraznih krležnih dijela

1340
00:46:11,880 --> 00:46:14,340
[SPEAKER_01] ovisno o nekakvim pojmovima

1341
00:46:14,340 --> 00:46:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] koje on tematizira

1342
00:46:15,420 --> 00:46:16,699
[SPEAKER_01] sličnoj repertoriji

1343
00:46:16,699 --> 00:46:17,460
[SPEAKER_01] u Maruliču,

1344
00:46:17,460 --> 00:46:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] samo sasvim druga stvar.

1345
00:46:18,920 --> 00:46:21,579
[SPEAKER_01] Krleža ne baš tako pohvalno

1346
00:46:21,579 --> 00:46:22,619
[SPEAKER_01] govori o Maruliču.

1347
00:46:22,619 --> 00:46:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] Krleža je gromada.

1348
00:46:25,900 --> 00:46:28,179
[SPEAKER_00] A, znate, gromada je

1349
00:46:28,179 --> 00:46:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] nešto što ne možete

1350
00:46:32,340 --> 00:46:33,519
[SPEAKER_00] mojiti mjesto

1351
00:46:33,519 --> 00:46:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] orijentacije,

1352
00:46:34,320 --> 00:46:35,860
[SPEAKER_00] a gromada može biti

1353
00:46:35,860 --> 00:46:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] nekad i zapreka.

1354
00:46:36,719 --> 00:46:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Krležu ne možete

1355
00:46:38,599 --> 00:46:39,320
[SPEAKER_00] mojići,

1356
00:46:39,320 --> 00:46:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] on je golem u svojim

1357
00:46:40,960 --> 00:46:43,840
[SPEAKER_00] pozitivnim stranjama

1358
00:46:43,840 --> 00:46:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] u svom književom dijelu,

1359
00:46:44,880 --> 00:46:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] a onda je nekad veliki

1360
00:46:46,880 --> 00:46:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] u svojim zabludama.

1361
00:46:49,199 --> 00:46:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje je riječ o očitoj intervenciji

1362
00:46:51,920 --> 00:46:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] Krležinovi, to smo doznali

1363
00:46:53,420 --> 00:46:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] zahvaljujući istraživanjima Davara Balića

1364
00:46:55,780 --> 00:46:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] koji je ušao u arhive akademijne

1365
00:46:58,519 --> 00:47:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] i našao sve što se moglo o tome naći.

1366
00:47:01,539 --> 00:47:06,619
[SPEAKER_00] Krleža je zatražio da se Filipovićev tekst izbaci

1367
00:47:06,619 --> 00:47:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] argumentacijom koja je

1368
00:47:08,880 --> 00:47:12,139
[SPEAKER_00] ideološka, kratko rečeno,

1369
00:47:12,139 --> 00:47:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] ali i za koje se

1370
00:47:14,360 --> 00:47:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] o mojem sudu krije i nešto sujete,

1371
00:47:17,260 --> 00:47:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] jer Filipović

1372
00:47:19,420 --> 00:47:23,320
[SPEAKER_00] ne puno i ne izrazito,

1373
00:47:23,320 --> 00:47:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] ali na jednom mjestu,

1374
00:47:24,360 --> 00:47:26,239
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo jasno kritizira Krležu.

1375
00:47:26,300 --> 00:47:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] I mislim da se Krleži temeljito

1376
00:47:29,440 --> 00:47:31,380
[SPEAKER_00] se time Krleži zamjerio,

1377
00:47:31,380 --> 00:47:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] a onda je on ovo drugo argumentirao,

1378
00:47:33,500 --> 00:47:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] onako kako argumentirao,

1379
00:47:34,960 --> 00:47:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] na nekakav način,

1380
00:47:36,599 --> 00:47:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] on je očekio od Marulića zapravo

1381
00:47:38,260 --> 00:47:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] da bude nekakav, ne znam,

1382
00:47:40,300 --> 00:47:41,739
[SPEAKER_00] protestant u ono vrijeme,

1383
00:47:41,739 --> 00:47:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] a ne da se umjesto,

1384
00:47:44,980 --> 00:47:46,360
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, Filipović kaže

1385
00:47:46,360 --> 00:47:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] ili islam ili kršćanstvo,

1386
00:47:47,659 --> 00:47:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] Marulić nije imao trećeg izbora,

1387
00:47:49,039 --> 00:47:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] a Krleža viće imao je trećeg izbora,

1388
00:47:51,199 --> 00:47:53,800
[SPEAKER_00] onda navodi razne kasnije naše autore

1389
00:47:53,800 --> 00:47:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji su se opredijeli od Vlačića

1390
00:47:55,420 --> 00:47:56,360
[SPEAKER_00] ili lirika i tako dalje

1391
00:47:56,360 --> 00:47:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] za tako zvanitveći put.

1392
00:47:57,599 --> 00:48:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] To je, ahistorijski je tako

1393
00:48:00,019 --> 00:48:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] promazvati stvari.

1394
00:48:01,119 --> 00:48:04,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ali istini za volju treba reći

1395
00:48:04,440 --> 00:48:06,300
[SPEAKER_00] da je, zahvaljujući kolegi Baliću,

1396
00:48:06,300 --> 00:48:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] smo doznali da je Krleža

1397
00:48:07,940 --> 00:48:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] mnogo puta se dotaknuo Marulića

1398
00:48:10,039 --> 00:48:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] i da je na više mjesta

1399
00:48:11,659 --> 00:48:15,019
[SPEAKER_00] taj njegov izraz bio pozitivan.

1400
00:48:15,019 --> 00:48:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] On je ipak Marulića cijenio

1401
00:48:17,260 --> 00:48:19,139
[SPEAKER_00] kao autora koji je otvorio

1402
00:48:19,139 --> 00:48:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] hrvatski jezik

1403
00:48:20,699 --> 00:48:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] o zbilnom pjesmičkom stvaranju,

1404
00:48:22,500 --> 00:48:24,639
[SPEAKER_00] koji je afirmirao i taj jezik

1405
00:48:24,639 --> 00:48:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] i ko ima i neke zasluge nacionalne,

1406
00:48:27,400 --> 00:48:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] ako hoćete.

1407
00:48:28,079 --> 00:48:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] Sve se to nalazi rasuto

1408
00:48:29,400 --> 00:48:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] u raznim drugim tekstovima

1409
00:48:32,539 --> 00:48:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] koji ne tematiziraju Marulića,

1410
00:48:34,539 --> 00:48:35,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji su često puni

1411
00:48:35,579 --> 00:48:36,780
[SPEAKER_00] vatrometne retorike

1412
00:48:36,780 --> 00:48:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] koje kod Krleže ima.

1413
00:48:38,260 --> 00:48:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] Samo jedna paralela Marulićeva,

1414
00:48:40,059 --> 00:48:41,099
[SPEAKER_01] Judita, Čakavica,

1415
00:48:41,099 --> 00:48:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] balade Petri Sekeren Puha.

1416
00:48:43,019 --> 00:48:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] Malim lijepo, to je odlična paralela Krleže.

1417
00:48:45,159 --> 00:48:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] Isto osjećao da ti naši jezici

1418
00:48:49,559 --> 00:48:51,360
[SPEAKER_00] koji su bili književni,

1419
00:48:51,360 --> 00:48:54,099
[SPEAKER_00] da je učinjena neka vrsta nepravde

1420
00:48:54,099 --> 00:48:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] što su oni ugašeni

1421
00:48:56,019 --> 00:48:58,639
[SPEAKER_00] kada je nužnom standardizacijom

1422
00:48:58,639 --> 00:49:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] proskribirana gotovo Čakavica i Kajkavica.

1423
00:49:02,860 --> 00:49:05,219
[SPEAKER_00] On je naprao jedan nevjerojatni čin

1424
00:49:05,219 --> 00:49:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] i pjesnički, kako god hoćete,

1425
00:49:07,639 --> 00:49:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] lingvistički čak svojim baladama.

1426
00:49:10,199 --> 00:49:13,280
[SPEAKER_00] Danas se naravno rehabilitira

1427
00:49:13,280 --> 00:49:14,639
[SPEAKER_00] Čakavica i Kajkavica

1428
00:49:14,639 --> 00:49:17,280
[SPEAKER_00] i to je korisno i potrebno,

1429
00:49:17,280 --> 00:49:20,260
[SPEAKER_00] ne dovodeći u pitanje potrebu standarda.

1430
00:49:20,260 --> 00:49:22,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, vidite, takav je Krleže

1431
00:49:22,780 --> 00:49:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] protuslovan i srećom Krleva.

1432
00:49:26,880 --> 00:49:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] Filipović je u tekstu spašen.

1433
00:49:28,519 --> 00:49:31,340
[SPEAKER_00] Filipović je jako dobro pogodio

1434
00:49:31,340 --> 00:49:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] neke aspekte Marulića

1435
00:49:33,079 --> 00:49:35,579
[SPEAKER_00] i neke motive Marulićevih izbora.

1436
00:49:35,579 --> 00:49:38,820
[SPEAKER_01] Marulićeva zavičajno snima refleksije

1437
00:49:38,820 --> 00:49:40,360
[SPEAKER_01] u suvremenu hrvatskoj književnosti.

1438
00:49:40,360 --> 00:49:41,460
[SPEAKER_01] Uzimljom samo za primjer,

1439
00:49:41,460 --> 00:49:42,599
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam koliko vam je poznato,

1440
00:49:42,599 --> 00:49:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] vjerojatno,

1441
00:49:43,019 --> 00:49:44,159
[SPEAKER_01] je možda najospijelijeg,

1442
00:49:44,159 --> 00:49:46,139
[SPEAKER_01] najčitanijeg trenutno hrvatskog pisica.

1443
00:49:46,139 --> 00:49:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] Riječ je o Kristijanu Novaku.

1444
00:49:47,380 --> 00:49:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1445
00:49:47,760 --> 00:49:48,920
[SPEAKER_01] Koji u svoje romane,

1446
00:49:48,920 --> 00:49:50,679
[SPEAKER_01] počeši od Črna mati zemla

1447
00:49:50,679 --> 00:49:52,079
[SPEAKER_01] do nedavnog romana,

1448
00:49:52,079 --> 00:49:54,440
[SPEAKER_01] koji se bavi jednim novinski izvještajem

1449
00:49:54,440 --> 00:49:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] kojeg on majstralno razveo

1450
00:49:56,960 --> 00:49:57,880
[SPEAKER_01] u jednom književno dijelo,

1451
00:49:57,880 --> 00:50:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] je utkao svoj međumuski kajkarski jezik.

1452
00:50:00,940 --> 00:50:01,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

1453
00:50:01,320 --> 00:50:04,260
[SPEAKER_01] I to je stvarno vrhunskog postignuća.

1454
00:50:04,260 --> 00:50:05,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kažem, riječ je ozbilja

1455
00:50:05,519 --> 00:50:07,699
[SPEAKER_01] najčitanijem i kritički najhvaljenijem.

1456
00:50:07,920 --> 00:50:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] Sada je on zaista najčitaniji.

1457
00:50:10,500 --> 00:50:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] To što nam jasno pokazuje

1458
00:50:14,800 --> 00:50:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] da ti lokalni jezici ili nariječja,

1459
00:50:18,039 --> 00:50:19,219
[SPEAKER_00] kako god hoćete,

1460
00:50:19,219 --> 00:50:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] da nisu zapreka.

1461
00:50:20,699 --> 00:50:22,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je književno dijelo dobro,

1462
00:50:22,179 --> 00:50:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] onda je to još jedna dodatna boja.

1463
00:50:24,699 --> 00:50:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] I za kraj Eho Marulića

1464
00:50:26,820 --> 00:50:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] u drugim velikanima.

1465
00:50:28,420 --> 00:50:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] Tin Ujević, oproštaj njegov.

1466
00:50:30,599 --> 00:50:31,280
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1467
00:50:31,280 --> 00:50:34,440
[SPEAKER_01] Pjesnički opus i Tonča Petrasova Marovića

1468
00:50:34,440 --> 00:50:36,940
[SPEAKER_01] i Jakšef Jamienga i tu kritika nalazi

1469
00:50:36,940 --> 00:50:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] od Ijeke Marulićeve.

1470
00:50:38,039 --> 00:50:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] I jedna, jedna roman.

1471
00:50:40,059 --> 00:50:41,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dina Milinović,

1472
00:50:41,699 --> 00:50:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] povisničara umjetnosti i književnika,

1473
00:50:43,920 --> 00:50:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] koji uzima Marulića

1474
00:50:45,400 --> 00:50:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] kao protagonistu svog romana.

1475
00:50:47,119 --> 00:50:48,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam, nekakva paralela.

1476
00:50:48,719 --> 00:50:50,159
[SPEAKER_01] Iako su paralela nezahvalne,

1477
00:50:50,159 --> 00:50:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] bila bi Umberto Eko i Ime Ruže.

1478
00:50:51,920 --> 00:50:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ima nekih sličnosti.

1479
00:50:55,619 --> 00:50:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] Inače, kada ste spomenuli,

1480
00:50:56,800 --> 00:50:58,719
[SPEAKER_00] treba naravno spomenuti i nazora.

1481
00:50:58,719 --> 00:51:01,360
[SPEAKER_00] Božete spomenuti i Luka Paljetka,

1482
00:51:01,360 --> 00:51:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji je isto jednog virtuoznu pjesmu

1483
00:51:02,719 --> 00:51:04,059
[SPEAKER_00] Maruliće u jeziku ispjevao.

1484
00:51:05,039 --> 00:51:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] Marulić je prisutan i u drami.

1485
00:51:06,880 --> 00:51:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] U Boris Senker ima farse,

1486
00:51:09,579 --> 00:51:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da bi se tako moglo definijati.

1487
00:51:11,360 --> 00:51:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tri glavosjeka, jedna od njih je posvećena Juditi.

1488
00:51:14,119 --> 00:51:16,320
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, Miro Gavran,

1489
00:51:16,320 --> 00:51:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] naravno, roman Judita,

1490
00:51:18,260 --> 00:51:21,199
[SPEAKER_00] koja se ne odnosi izravno na Marulića,

1491
00:51:21,199 --> 00:51:23,219
[SPEAKER_00] ali neminovno nas asociira.

1492
00:51:23,219 --> 00:51:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dino Milinović je napravio nešto,

1493
00:51:25,880 --> 00:51:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] zaista na neki način,

1494
00:51:27,400 --> 00:51:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] u Ekovskom smislu,

1495
00:51:29,579 --> 00:51:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] napravio neku vrstu povijesnog krimića,

1496
00:51:32,019 --> 00:51:33,559
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem je Marulić važan lik,

1497
00:51:33,559 --> 00:51:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] rekonstruirao je cijelu jednu epohu,

1498
00:51:35,480 --> 00:51:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] da pa će vratio se u vrijeme Dioklecijana,

1499
00:51:39,239 --> 00:51:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] zaista ne samo eruditski,

1500
00:51:43,940 --> 00:51:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] nego i književno izveo jednu liniju,

1501
00:51:48,039 --> 00:51:51,820
[SPEAKER_00] koja nam govori koliko Marulić može biti intrigantan.

1502
00:51:51,820 --> 00:51:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] I svojim životom, ne samo svojim dijelom.

1503
00:51:53,880 --> 00:51:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] Da, biografije su napisane.

1504
00:51:56,159 --> 00:51:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] Što mislite o mogućnosti da se na jedan obimni,

1505
00:51:59,380 --> 00:52:01,559
[SPEAKER_01] znanstveno-akribni način,

1506
00:52:01,559 --> 00:52:04,440
[SPEAKER_01] sistematski način napiše biografija Marulića?

1507
00:52:06,440 --> 00:52:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] To nije lako napraviti,

1508
00:52:08,039 --> 00:52:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] to se može napraviti mnoga mjesta

1509
00:52:12,199 --> 00:52:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] u Marulićoj biografiji su zagonetna,

1510
00:52:15,199 --> 00:52:18,179
[SPEAKER_00] i u bibliografiji također.

1511
00:52:18,179 --> 00:52:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] A neobično mnogo toga znamo.

1512
00:52:21,059 --> 00:52:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] Raspored toga što znamo i što je, ne znamo,

1513
00:52:23,139 --> 00:52:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] mogli bismo reći nepravedan.

1514
00:52:24,900 --> 00:52:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ako bismo rekli što bismo htjeli znati,

1515
00:52:27,480 --> 00:52:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] biste rekli ne znamo ili studirao.

1516
00:52:29,619 --> 00:52:32,360
[SPEAKER_00] Zaista ne znamo, ne nekakvog traga da je studirao.

1517
00:52:32,360 --> 00:52:32,739
[SPEAKER_00] I gdje.

1518
00:52:32,739 --> 00:52:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] Englezi još manje o Šekspiru, pa ne smije.

1519
00:52:34,980 --> 00:52:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali možemo s druge strane biti sretni u navodnoj nepravdi.

1520
00:52:41,019 --> 00:52:43,679
[SPEAKER_00] Mi znamo, recimo, anegdoksi govoreći,

1521
00:52:43,679 --> 00:52:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] znamo točan datum Marulićeva rođenja i Marulićeve smrti.

1522
00:52:47,480 --> 00:52:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ste pisa koji je živio prije petstotina godina.

1523
00:52:50,300 --> 00:52:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] To nije samo razumljivo i to treba isto osvestiti.

1524
00:52:53,119 --> 00:52:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ne znamo za Šekspira datum rađenja, znamo kad je kršten.

1525
00:52:56,619 --> 00:52:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] Za Danteja znamo godinu i znamo u kojem horoskopskom znaku.

1526
00:52:59,960 --> 00:53:06,739
[SPEAKER_00] Za Erasma Rotterdanskog ne znamo, govori se negdje od 466. do 469.

1527
00:53:06,739 --> 00:53:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, za tako važne pisa u kojima su napisane biblioteke, knjiga,

1528
00:53:10,940 --> 00:53:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] sve je istraženo što se moglo istražiti.

1529
00:53:13,039 --> 00:53:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ovdje imamo i znamo i znamo kako znamo.

1530
00:53:16,559 --> 00:53:20,280
[SPEAKER_00] Neobično važno pitanje, kad se bavite povijesnim provučavanjem,

1531
00:53:20,300 --> 00:53:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] kako znamo to što znamo.

1532
00:53:22,059 --> 00:53:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] U redu, profesore, hvala vam na vašem sudjelovanju

1533
00:53:25,019 --> 00:53:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] i nadam se da će naš razgovor biti pocicajan našim gledateljima.

1534
00:53:28,019 --> 00:53:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vama na pitanjima i ja se nadam da smo malo osvijetlili Marulića.

